title: Phil Collins autobiography to be published in 2016
text: > Entertainment Phil Collins autobiography to be published in 2016 FILE - In this Aug. 26, 2010 file photo, musician Phil Collins poses for a portrait in New York. Against all odds, Phil Collins has decided to write an autobiography. The former Genesis drummer and 1980s icon is one of pop musicâ€™s best-selling artists, with hits including "In the Air Tonight" and "Against All Odds." Collins said in a statement Monday, Tuesday, Oct. 2015 that he had been asked several times to write a memoir "but never felt that the time was right _ until now." (AP Photo/Victoria Will, File)
